<OUTPUT_TEXT>Dear [Customer],

Thank you for bringing this matter to our attention. After reviewing your concerns, I regret to inform you that we are unable to resolve the issue within our department. The matter has been referred to our [Designated Department, e.g., Quality Assurance, Product Development, etc.] for further investigation and resolution.

We will ensure that your concerns are thoroughly examined and addressed in a timely manner. You will be notified of any updates or developments as soon as possible.

Please feel free to contact me if you have any further questions or concerns. Your satisfaction is our top priority, and we appreciate your patience and cooperation in this matter.

Sincerely,
[Your Name]
Senior Customer Service Representative</OUTPUT_TEXT>
